org.apache.drill.exec.store.easy.json.loader

Class TestUnknowns

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.test.DrillTest
        • org.apache.drill.test.SubOperatorTest
          • org.apache.drill.exec.store.easy.json.loader.BaseJsonLoaderTest
            • org.apache.drill.exec.store.easy.json.loader.TestUnknowns

  • public class TestUnknowns
extends BaseJsonLoaderTest
    Tests the ability of the JSON reader to "wait out" a set of leading null or empty array values to wait until an actual value appears before deciding on the column type. Hitting the end of batch, or an array that contains only null values, forces resolution to VARCHAR.
